div.row(ng-controller='QueueCtrl')
  div.col-md-12
    form(role='form').form-horizontal
      h3 AWS Queue
      div.well
        div.form-group
          label.control-label.col-md-2(for='poll') Polling period
          div.col-md-2
            input#poll.form-control(type='text', placeholder='Time in seconds', ng-model='queue.poll')
        div.form-group
          label.control-label.col-md-2(for='queue') Queue info
          div.col-md-5
            input#queue.form-control(type='text', placeholder='Name of the queue on SQS', ng-model='queue.name')
          div.col-md-5
            input#region.form-control(type='text', placeholder='Name of AWS region', ng-model='queue.region')
        div.form-group
          label.control-label.col-md-2(for='key') Authentication
          div.col-md-5
            input#key.form-control(type='password', placeholder='SQS Access Key', ng-model='queue.accessKey')
          div.col-md-5
            input#secret.form-control(type='password', placeholder='SQS Secret Key', ng-model='queue.secretKey')
        div.form-group
          div.col-md-offset-2.col-md-10
            span.help-block The credentials above will not be saved in the configuration file. Instead am environment variable will be setup.
        +saveConfig('save()')